\begin_inset Formula $\dim A\left(W\right)=\dim\left\{ B_{V^{*}}\backslash\left\{ f_{i},...,f_{j}\right\} \right\} =\left|B_{V^{*}}\right|-\left|\left\{ f_{i},...,f_{j}\right\} \right|=\dim V^{*}-\dim W=\dim V-\dim W$
